  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/4259b8f47e095c118168131fef72f0c2.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/4259b8f47e095c118168131fef72f0c2.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/4259b8f47e095c118168131fef72f0c2.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>SOS OPS!</strong> is a co-op chaos game about saving a city, where you and your friends turn every mission into absolute madness.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/39c1bed6aa69a2c29aeb299db9df7585.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/39c1bed6aa69a2c29aeb299db9df7585.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/39c1bed6aa69a2c29aeb299db9df7585.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>MAJOR UPDATE: PvP MODE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brand-new way to ruin friendships.<br>Pick an arena on the in-game computer and jump straight into the fight.<br>Set the rules by yourself: time limit, kill goal, infinite mode, gear spawn rate.<br>Weapons & power-ups spawn on the map and then you lose them on death.<br>5 arenas to start: Volcano Crater, SOS Factory, Flight 747, Pyramid, Tower<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/14a219eda9ba9c3fd590bc95de74cadf.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/14a219eda9ba9c3fd590bc95de74cadf.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/14a219eda9ba9c3fd590bc95de74cadf.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You’re a team of emergency responders.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In practice, that means you’re <i>at least trying</i> to be one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Someone’s putting out a fire, someone’s carrying a cat, someone accidentally drops a teammate off a roof, and someone else has no idea what the objective is — but they’re doing their best. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/e31d59ed0bc09cbf765e4e790d61b40a.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/e31d59ed0bc09cbf765e4e790d61b40a.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/e31d59ed0bc09cbf765e4e790d61b40a.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Physics is the thing you’ll either love us for or absolutely hate us for.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It breaks plans, creates ridiculous situations, and turns even the simplest actions into a chain of failures, shouting (and sometimes… victories). </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/6f98213f813aad3ee0485ac53d0960a9.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/6f98213f813aad3ee0485ac53d0960a9.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>No boring tutorials. No tedious tasks.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was made by ADHD people, for ADHD people. Just fast-paced missions, constant movement, and a lot of falling over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/dc5cca9f78aaa8f59375abdd9f89f390.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/dc5cca9f78aaa8f59375abdd9f89f390.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/dc5cca9f78aaa8f59375abdd9f89f390.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Grab a team of up to 4 players and dive into the city chaos, where success isn’t measured by completed levels — but by how loud you’re laughing.<strong> </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/6e4fe3c1d3b989ab9e7d2947460da206.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/6e4fe3c1d3b989ab9e7d2947460da206.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/6e4fe3c1d3b989ab9e7d2947460da206.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/4259b8f47e095c118168131fef72f0c2.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/4259b8f47e095c118168131fef72f0c2.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/4259b8f47e095c118168131fef72f0c2.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>SOS OPS!</strong> is a co-op chaos game about saving a city, where you and your friends turn every mission into absolute madness.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/39c1bed6aa69a2c29aeb299db9df7585.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/39c1bed6aa69a2c29aeb299db9df7585.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/39c1bed6aa69a2c29aeb299db9df7585.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>MAJOR UPDATE: PvP MODE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brand-new way to ruin friendships.<br>Pick an arena on the in-game computer and jump straight into the fight.<br>Set the rules by yourself: time limit, kill goal, infinite mode, gear spawn rate.<br>Weapons & power-ups spawn on the map and then you lose them on death.<br>5 arenas to start: Volcano Crater, SOS Factory, Flight 747, Pyramid, Tower<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass