5ac53d0960a9.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/6f98213f813aad3ee0485ac53d0960a9.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>No boring tutorials. No tedious tasks.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was made by ADHD people, for ADHD people. Just fast-paced missions, constant movement, and a lot of falling over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/dc5cca9f78aaa8f59375abdd9f89f390.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/dc5cca9f78aaa8f59375abdd9f89f390.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/dc5cca9f78aaa8f59375abdd9f89f390.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Grab a team of up to 4 players and dive into the city chaos, where success isn’t measured by completed levels — but by how loud you’re laughing.<strong> </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/6e4fe3c1d3b989ab9e7d2947460da206.poster.avif?t=1772787100\" width=1138 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/6e4fe3c1d3b989ab9e7d2947460da206.webm?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475460/extras/6e4fe3c1d3b989ab9e7d2947460da206.mp4?t=1772787100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
